			<h3>Dental Fillings</h3> 
			<p>
				A filling is dental restorative material used to restore a tooth with structural loss to its normal condition in health, function, and appearance.  
			</p>
			<%= image_tag 'filling.jpg', :class => "float-right" %>	
			<h6><b>Fillings</b></h6>
			<ul>
				<li>Remove tooth decay</li>
				<li>Deter future tooth decay</li>
				<li>Reduce risk of infecting other people with cavity causing bacteria</li>
				<li>Reduce infection causing bad breath</li>
				<li>Reduce infection causing inflammations that threaten general health</li>
				<li>Restore tooth structure lost to infection</li>
				<li>Replace missing, worn, cracked, leaking, and discolored fillings</li>
				<li>Restore cracked and broken teeth</li>
				<li>Restore worn teeth</li>
